I‚Äôve been long $AMZN for ~3 years now, but quoting EBITDA for this business and saying it‚Äôs cheap tells you a lot about the investor, not the cheapness. EBIT and FCF are the realities here. It‚Äôs an asset heavy business with huge logistics and real depreciation costs. Chill!
